Notes for scaling

How to gallery uploads
    Option 1
        is upload thro django which is fine for now and testing
        e.g django will validate max size etc as well

    Option 2
        frontend sends image/s quantity and details to django -> django replies with presign storage links(think s3 or similar)
        frontend uploads via links
        frontend sends result of uploads  like, location for iamges, urls etc or any errors


How get embedding for face reg
    Option 1
        this only works if people have to sign up!!
        send none uploader user image/s to django and process in background
        then send an email when done
        and user can find there images
        can have a model to match user id, image and potentially gallery for better searching

    Option 2 which is optimized version
        upload iamge/s to django
        maybe 5 to 10 secs to do embeddings
        streaming / paginating images found for gallery on the frontend
